<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/jobdesc.css">
    <title>Retro-Craft Hub</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato&family=Roboto+Mono&family=Roboto:wght@500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
</head>
<body>

<div class="page-body">
    <div id="profile-container">
        <img id="profile-image" src="images/profile-image.jpg" alt="Profile Image" class="img-fluid">
        <h2 id="profile-name" class="mt-3 ml-4">Mr Bark</h2>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-dark mt-5 flex-column">
            <div class="navitems" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/userhome">Home </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/profile">View Profile</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/view-requests">Current Requests</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/job-page">Jobs</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="user-content">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
            <h3 class="header-title">Job Description</h3>              
            <br>
            <div class="card mb-4">
              <div class="card-body">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-sm-2">
                    <p class="mb-0">Name</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-sm-10">
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">Nignog Bing Bong</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <hr>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-sm-2">
                    <p class="mb-0"> Description </p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-sm-10">
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0"> Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Illum, eaque nostrum eius sequi consequatur culpa debitis molestiae, eos mollitia error, architecto sed excepturi dolores repudiandae corrupti quos ratione nihil adipisci!</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <hr>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-sm-2">
                    <p class="mb-0"> Required skills</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-sm-10">
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nihil vel neque tempore blanditiis temporibus illo ipsum necessitatibus quas amet culpa molestias corrupti aperiam unde veritatis est nobis earum, omnis impedit.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <hr>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-sm-2">
                    <p class="mb-0">Job details</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-sm-10">
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Molestias impedit non placeat omnis. Eius exercitationem labore qui fuga voluptates sequi, itaque dignissimos doloremque possimus similique molestiae culpa saepe amet sit.</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <hr>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-sm-2">
                    <p class="mb-0">Job Profile</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-sm-10">
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0"> All my fellas</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <hr>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-sm-2">
                    <p class="mb-0">Expected Time</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-sm-10">
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">Eternity</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <hr>
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-sm-2">
                    <p class="mb-0">Expected Pay</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-sm-10">
                    <p class="text-muted mb-0">2 dimes</p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-12">
          <h3 class="header-title">Producer Information</h3>
          <br>
          <div class="card mb-4">
            <div class="card-body">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-2">
                  <p class="mb-0">Full Name</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                  <p class="text-muted mb-0">{{userinfo.name}}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <hr>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-2">
                  <p class="mb-0">Email</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                  <p class="text-muted mb-0">{{userinfo.email}}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <hr>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-2">
                  <p class="mb-0">Phone</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                  <p class="text-muted mb-0">{{userinfo.phone}}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <hr>
              <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-2">
                  <p class="mb-0">Address</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-10">
                  <p class="text-muted mb-0">{{userinfo.address}}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.11.6/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

</body>
</html>